    "testimony": [
        [
            "AGNESS MAMSARENI MAGAWANA",
            "(sworn states)",
            "Unknown"
        ],
        [
            "ADV SANDI",
            "You are going to talk about Barnabas Mhlati Magawana.   How are you related?",
            "Unknown"
        ],
        [
            "AGNESS MAMSARENI MAGAWANA",
            "He was my elder brother.",
            "Female"
        ],
        [
            "ADV SANDI",
            "You say that he was executed in Pretoria.\nWhy was he hanged?",
            "Unknown"
        ],
        [
            "AGNESS MAMSARENI MAGAWANA",
            "They came to look for him at his home.  He was not here.   Only the wife was there.  They then ordered the wife to leave.  The wife left and went back to her own home.\n On the Wednesday he went to look for his wife.  That is the day that they detained him.",
            "Female"
        ],
        [
            "ADV SANDI",
            "So he was detained at his wife's home?",
            "Unknown"
        ],
        [
            "AGNESS MAMSARENI MAGAWANA",
            "Yes.",
            "Female"
        ],
        [
            "ADV SANDI",
            "Was he detained because he was an ANC member?",
            "Unknown"
        ],
        [
            "AGNESS MAMSARENI MAGAWANA",
            "Yes.  He would open the meeting with prayer when there was a Congo meeting.",
            "Female"
        ],
        [
            "ADV SANDI",
            "You say that there was a court case in Kokstad.  Was there a court case in Kokstad?",
            "Unknown"
        ],
        [
            "AGNESS MAMSARENI MAGAWANA",
            "I do not remember that...  Yes he was detained Bizana, then Kokstad, then Pretoria.",
            "Female"
        ],
        [
            "ADV SANDI",
            "Who was he with?",
            "Unknown"
        ],
        [
            "AGNESS MAMSARENI MAGAWANA",
            "Douglas as well.",
            "Female"
        ],
        [
            "ADV SANDI",
            "What were they accused of?",
            "Unknown"
        ],
        [
            "AGNESS MAMSARENI MAGAWANA",
            "Apparently they had killed a Chief.",
            "Female"
        ],
        [
            "ADV SANDI",
            "What was the name of the Chief?",
            "Unknown"
        ],
        [
            "AGNESS MAMSARENI MAGAWANA",
            "Chief Stanford.",
            "Female"
        ],
        [
            "ADV SANDI",
            "Did you see him before he was executed?",
            "Unknown"
        ],
        [
            "AGNESS MAMSARENI MAGAWANA",
            "Yes, some of my other brothers went.  We could not afford to go.",
            "Female"
        ],
        [
            "ADV SANDI",
            "Your request is that he should be exhumed and buried at home?  Do you have another request?",
            "Unknown"
        ],
        [
            "AGNESS MAMSARENI MAGAWANA",
            "If the Government could give us some form of compensation, because we lost a brother.",
            "Female"
        ],
        [
            "ADV SANDI",
            "You need compensation?",
            "Unknown"
        ],
        [
            "AGNESS MAMSARENI MAGAWANA",
            "Yes, whatever compensation they can give us.",
            "Female"
        ],
        [
            "ADV SANDI",
            "Is that all?",
            "Unknown"
        ],
        [
            "AGNESS MAMSARENI MAGAWANA",
            "Yes that is all Sir.",
            "Female"
        ]
    ]
}